{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">JOIN THE COMMUNITY &amp; FOLLOW DEVELOPMENT!</h2><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547890/extras/MM_Steam_About.png?t=1708628773\" /><br>Mecha Mayhem is a rogue-like fighting game within a world of battling mech-suits on a distant, warring world. You begin as M0nty, a simple ground maintenance droid\u2026 that happens to be compatible with every mechanical part and weapon available on the planet! Mix and match each body part in the game to build your own personal war machine and decide what faction should rule by taking out high-ranking enemy mechs!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547890/extras/Recording2024-01-02123017-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1708628773\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547890/extras/MM_Steam_Physics.png?t=1708628773\" /><br>\u2022 Rip enemies apart and use their severed limbs against them in our full dismemberment system<br>\u2022 Using a combination of weaponry, hand-to-hand combat and the hazadrous environment to defeat your enemies<br>\u2022 Play to unlock more weapons and gadgets<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547890/extras/bigswing.gif?t=1708628773\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547890/extras/MM_Steam_Mechs.png?t=1708628773\" /><br>\u2022 Full suit customization for your mech fighter<br>\u2022 Each part comes with its own unique ability, allowing combo-based attacks<br>\u2022 Over 3003 combinations, already in the play-test with much more to come!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547890/extras/011122-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1708628773\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb